    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use your radiant chakra on yourself, supercharging your chakra flow at the expense of your own health. For the duration, add one damage die to weapon attacks and jutsu you cast, twice per turn, and also for the duration you take 1d8 necrotic damage that cannot be reduced by any means at the start of each of your turns. You may end this jutsu as a bonus action.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. Starting at A-rank, increase the damage die of jutsu you cast and weapon attacks by 1.</p>",
